parameters.name: job
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (arn) of the world export job to describe.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the world export job.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The status of the world export job.

nested_items.name: createdAt
nested_items.description: The time, in milliseconds since the epoch, when the world export job was created.

nested_items.name: failureCode
nested_items.description: The failure code of the world export job if it failed:

nested_items.name: failureReason
nested_items.description: The reason why the world export job failed.

nested_items.name: clientRequestToken
nested_items.description: Unique, case-sensitive identifier that you provide to ensure the idempotency of the request.

nested_items.name: worlds
nested_items.description: A list of Amazon Resource Names (arns) that correspond to worlds to be exported.

nested_items.name: s3Prefix
nested_items.description: The S3 folder in the s3Bucket where output files will be placed.

nested_items.name: iamRole
nested_items.description: The IAM role that the world export process uses to access the Amazon S3 bucket and put the export.
